data.description: Take a look at this tastefully updated three bedroom home with a spacious living room and a convenient main floor laundry room. The kitchen has been updated with new counter tops, painted cabinet, flooring, sink, and appliances. 2 bedrooms on the upper level, one offers a walk in closet. There is no lack of natural light in this home and you will be very surprised by how energy efficient this home is. Many updates including but not limited- bathroom remodeled in 2022, roof in 2017, new LVP flooring and carpet in 2022, laundry room remodel in 2022, new paint, replacement windows, professionally clean duct work. Call your Realtor for a private showing!
